original_title: Prezydent N.R.D. Wilhelm Pieck w Warszawie
overview: This reportage is focused on Wilhelm Pieck’s visit in Warsaw in 1950. He was the president of East Germany between 1949 and 1960. The visit sealed diplomatic relations between the Polish People's Republic and the newly established German Democratic Republic (1949).
title: The President of the GDR Wilhelm Pieck in Warsaw
